1. *Nožem* sam isekao hleb na tanke kriške. (I sliced the bread into thin slices with a knife.)
2. Kuhinjski *noževi* su ostali neupotrebljeni nakon što smo završili sa pripremom hrane. (The kitchen knives remained unused after we finished preparing the food.)
3. Tražio sam *noževe* po kući kako bih otvorio paket. (I looked for knives around the house to open the package.)
4. *Nožićem* sam isekao etiketu sa odeće. (I cut the label off the clothes with a small knife.)
5. Držao je *nož* u ruci dok je seckao povrće. (He held a knife in his hand while he was chopping vegetables.)
6. *Nožem* za sečenje mesa isekao sam odrezak na male komade. (I cut the steak into small pieces with a meat-cutting knife.)
7. Dok sam prao sudove, slučajno sam se posekao *nožem*. (While washing the dishes, I accidentally cut myself with a knife.)
8. Majstor je precizno urezao slova u drvo koristeći *nožić*. (The craftsman carved letters into the wood precisely using a small knife.)
9. *Nožem* za kuvanje sam iseckao luk na sitne kockice. (I chopped the onion into small cubes with a cooking knife.)
10. Policajac je pretresao osumnjičenog i pronašao *nož* u njegovom džepu. (The police officer searched the suspect and found a knife in his pocket.)